"(define (fp-LQFP ct)

  (match-let ([(list width pitch)
               (case ct
                 ;; FIXME not all of them
                 ;; FIXME there can be multiple footprints for a ct
                 [(36) '(7 0.65)]
                 [(44) '(10 0.8)]
                 [(48) '(7 0.5)])])
    (kicad-helper "Package_QFP.pretty/"
                  (~a "LQFP-" ct "_" width "x" width
                      "mm_P" pitch "mm.kicad_mod"))))"
